HEADWORD: Sweetweed
<hw>Sweet"weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A name for two tropical American weeds (<spn>Capraria
biflora</spn>, and <spn>Scoparia dulcis</spn>) of the Figwort
family.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

